dcp_projectbrief: This is a private application by Waterview at Greenpoint LLC, pursuant to Section 11-43 ZR requesting a renewal of a special permit (C 140047 ZSK) for a three year term, and renewal of two authorizations (N 140048 ZAK and N 140049 ZAK) to facilitate the development of 720 units of housing, including 200 affordable units, and ground floor retail, located within three 30- to 40-story buildings at 77 Commercial Street in Greenpoint, Community District 1, Brooklyn.
